---
title: Honey Mustard-Glazed Chicken with Baked Veggies
description: Parsley, rosemary, and thyme? Yes, we’re going there. This power trio of herbs is used to enhance the flavor of roasted winter veggies in this recipe, as well as to make a flavorful pan sauce that gets drizzled over everything. Served with brown rice, it’s a healthy, fortifying meal that’ll help you stay energized through the week.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/au-honey-mustard-chicken-w01-fam-d41f58bd.jpg
